{"tid":1436812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【團結先會勝利】大台係我哋呢啲雨革老鬼嘅PTSD黎","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T02:42:33.000Z","uid":223260,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8278098e38d9589300b5f3e796d5aeb1e16545bd","tid":1436812,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"各位近排出世嘅手足，<br />\n可能唔知道雨革發生咩事。<br />\n當年就係因爲大台令抗爭者嚴重分裂，<br />\n詳情可以參考下呢個post：<br />\n<br />\n有冇老鬼可以講下 14年嗰陣 係點樣輸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434013</a><br />\n<br />\n大台最主要嘅問題係壟斷話語權，<br />\n令某啲抗爭者比其他抗爭者有更大權力。<br />\n更加嚴重嘅甚至篤勇武派灰同警察報串。<br />\n之後更加演變到要拆大台，勇武派抗爭者圍住大台屌。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係呢個post唔係想翻舊賬，而係想解決問題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實每個手足對成個運動嘅立場，甚至每個行動嘅睇法都有差異。<br />\n有啲可能甚至係水火不容嘅，恨不得另一派人消失。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">但能夠包容所有差異，我地先會強大。</span><br />\n<br />\n但係宜家出現咗個問題，<br />\n就係反大台嘅人屌大台，<br />\n有啲人又屌反大台嘅人分化。<br />\n咁樣互屌本身已經係非常分化。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">反大台嘅手足你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</span></span><br />\n如果堅持宜家即刻同泛民割蓆，<br />\n翻曬啲舊賬出嚟全面開戰嘅話，<br />\n好快就會時光倒流返去14年咁。<br />\n<br />\n我認同大台係絕對唔應該存在，<br />\n但係泛民鬼極都坐擁龐大嘅支持，<br />\n宜家係極其嚴峻嘅時刻，<br />\n輸咗就全面監控萬劫不復必死無疑。<br />\n次要敵人如果可以嘅話都要we connect。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我認爲應該逼使佢地歸隊反大台，</span></span><br />\n正如七月一衝立會宜家已經冇人敢割蓆。<br />\n唔好將想建立大台嘅人標籤做【泛民】，<br />\n而係孤立佢哋，等其他泛民唔敢跟。<br />\n要清算留返勝利後煲底慶祝完先清算。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">覺得反大台係分化嘅手足你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</span></span><br />\n大台係我哋呢啲雨革老鬼嘅PTSD黎，<br />\n如果有人反應太激烈請包容下。<br />\n如果閣下唔明白有啲人點解咁大反應，<br />\n可以去瞭解下14年嘅歷史，<br />\n唔好一黎就話人三毛，好傷人感情。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我認爲大台係絕對唔應該存在，<br />\n因爲只會將手足劃分階級，<br />\n大台只會有一個立場，<br />\n但一衆手足有千千萬萬個諗法，<br />\n所以大台支持邊個諗法都好，都會出現分化。<br />\n而且有大台政府就有明確target可以打，<br />\n打散咗民氣就散，返唔到轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n所以時刻警惕，<br />\n唔好俾疑似大台，糾察，呢啲會分階級嘅野出現。<br />\n互相提醒，時刻警惕。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆，求求大家，香港人一定要贏。</span></span>"},{"pid":"db56ad21b8f49335b8c139a7912310ce8456f101","tid":1436812,"uid":36378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe505f9fb25bb236fadd7c643fcf8895d26e62ab","tid":1436812,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db56ad21b8f49335b8c139a7912310ce8456f101","tid":1436812,"uid":36378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662f6edbd47d8862d9f7f449dc8c060d0ab2d959","tid":1436812,"uid":4050,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解一定係佢地開主題我地曬時間去駁佢？ 點解唔係我地開主題佢地之後回應我地</strong>？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想知<span style=\"color: green;\">鐳射筆，外國勢力，大台，經濟差</span><br />\n<br />\n想知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>葉虎，同志們，過期彈呀</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9c972c324d18cb64821a0a13d65e512ec7e50bea","tid":1436812,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"662f6edbd47d8862d9f7f449dc8c060d0ab2d959","tid":1436812,"uid":4050,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解一定係佢地開主題我地曬時間去駁佢？ 點解唔係我地開主題佢地之後回應我地</strong>？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想知<span style=\"color: green;\">鐳射筆，外國勢力，大台，經濟差</span><br />\n<br />\n想知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>葉虎，同志們，過期彈呀</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"近排太多瑣事post，popo講咩777講咩真係唔多想知，葉虎，同志們，過期彈三單野都未清算。"},{"pid":"33fd63f59274e5aed092534f6a61eb8799f4861c","tid":1436812,"uid":67023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"雨革完咗好耐都唔敢再去夏慤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a9180ec4e6223bae63900f9d7d5f69ac18b12a","tid":1436812,"uid":25164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3d83363b1199beb376fdeede8cc3fa074e6e86","tid":1436812,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33fd63f59274e5aed092534f6a61eb8799f4861c","tid":1436812,"uid":67023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"雨革完咗好耐都唔敢再去夏慤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bb57dfc96341f82bc943dbe6df9ca12cd42f30","tid":1436812,"uid":37922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bc94204bca2765ef98bc1b0f2041ade1823fd6f","tid":1436812,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9a986376d1905eaee1d68874a2ca79ef11c2c2","tid":1436812,"uid":186836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好"},{"pid":"67383a0b4f3dfa7313922d4e334dc42b31330c3f","ti